value.string: You will love the stunning ocean views from this great Kapalua oceanfront 2 bedroom, 3 bathroom condominium. Location, location, location. This precious single level property has arguably the best location at the Kapalua Bay Villas. Extremely popular vacation rental unit. Come see for yourself and you'll see why. Comfort at a higher level, it's a perfect home to relax and enjoy the best Kapalua Resort has to offer.

This custom home is a high end ocean front residence with the best views on the North Shore of Maui. As one enters they are engulfed with the deep blue ocean and the vistas from the lanai stretch from Paia Bay to Kahakuloa to the west and Hookipa to the east. The home has 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths and includes a detached caretaker’s home of 1 bedroom/1bath and 600 sq ft of living area. This beach style estate commands the view from the point of land on approximately 29,000. The home is built with quality materials with fine craftsmanship and privacy in mind. This is a one of a kind property and a rare opportunity to own a jewel in Paia with the security of a gated driveway in an upscale development. Come join us for a showing of this beautiful property today! Listor must be present for all showings. Tenant occupied. Please allow 24 hours for showings.
